==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sumbul
<hw>Sum"bul</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pers.]</ety> <def>The
musky root of an Asiatic umbelliferous plant, <spn>Ferula Sumbul</spn>.
It is used in medicine as a stimulant.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>sumbal</asp>.]</altsp> -- <wordforms><wf>Sum*bul"ic</wf>,
<pos>a.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sumerian</ent>⟦br⟧
